name: Individual Double Tris
description:
Individual Double Tris with a seed based on the owners tezos-addresses, renders differently for every owner.

Click/Tap to cycle through the different versions of the different owners.
Use Arrow-Down to toggle clearing-mode.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.collide and p5.createloop.
- @TeNinEightNFTs
